    "Here, we list three future directions where LoRA will be indispensable.",
    "LoRA for GaaSIn Generative-as-a-Service (GaaS), cloud-based platforms provide users with generative artificial intelligence (AGI) services.",
    "GaaS enables users enjoy AGI without deploying local computational resources.",
    "For the users' needs are diverse, it is necessary to provides various functions for GaaS.",
    "To implement the various functions, we can construct a LoRA module for each function."
